      <h1 class='title'>Small Retail Businesses</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c248WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_248ws' title='Col. 248WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c248WS' name='column_248ws' href='#column_248ws' rel='bookmark'>248WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06170'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_199'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-nigel-evans' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_199' title='Link to this speech by Mr Nigel Evans' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-nigel-evans" title="Mr Nigel Evans">Mr. Evans</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06170">To ask the Secretary of State for Trade and Industry what estimates she has made of the value of small retail businesses to the UK economy. [88645]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06171'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_200'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-nigel-griffiths' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_200' title='Link to this speech by Mr Nigel Griffiths' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-nigel-griffiths" title="Mr Nigel Griffiths">Nigel Griffiths</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06171"> <span class="italic">[holding answer 7 January 2003]:</span> Small and medium-sized enterprises are critical to the UK economy, generating new jobs and contributing to over half of the UK business revenue. Recent figures estimate there were 3.7 million enterprises employing nearly 23 million people, and with an annual turnover of over &#x00A3;2 trillion. Small retail businesses (sector 52 with 0 to 249 employees) represent 8 per cent. of all enterprises, 5 per cent. of all work force jobs and account for 4 per cent. of the UK turnover.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
